1. s3-creation:
   search s3 --> Create bucket --> General purpose --> Bucket name(masthan8985745) --> Bucket Versioning(Enable) --> create bucket.

2. presigned URL creation: [for everyone image access limited time]
   image(tick) --> actions(share with a presigned URL) --> Minutes(1) or Hours(1) --> create presigned URL.

3. make public particular bucket:
    1. search s3 --> Permissions --> Block public access (bucket settings) Edit --> Block all public access(un-tick) --> save changes. 
    2. Permissions --> Object Ownership(edit) --> ACLs enabled(tick) --> I acknowledge that ACLs will be restored(tick) --> save changes. 
    3. image(tick) --> Actions --> make publick using ACL --> make public. 
